'''Main Event Entertainment, LP''' operates [[Family entertainment center|family entertainment centers]] headquartered in [[Plano, Texas]] with locations throughout the [[United States]]. The company is owned and operated by  the Australian leisure company, [[Ardent Leisure]].

== Overview ==
Main Event Entertainment™ operates family entertainment centers which feature [[Cue sports|billiards]], [[bowling]], [[Arcade game|arcade games]], [[laser tag]], [[rock climbing]], [[Miniature golf|mini golf]], gravity ropes course, and [[karaoke]]. Main Event offers facilities and services for [[Birthday|birthday parties]]. The company also provides food and beverage, as well as meeting and event space with accommodations for corporate meetings or group gatherings; and event facility rental services. Main Event Entertainment™ was founded in 1998 and is based in Plano, Texas, with locations throughout the [[United States]]. Main Event competes with [[Dave & Buster's|Dave & Busters]] , EVO Entertainment, and [[Topgolf|TopGolf]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.owler.com/company/mainevent|title=Main Event Entertainment Competitors, Revenue and Employees - Owler Company Profile|website=Owler|language=en|access-date=2018-08-16}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/guests-can-head-for-fun-at-main-event-entertainments-second-chicago-area-location-300318549.html|title=Guests Can Head For Fun At Main Event Entertainment's Second Chicago-Area Location|website=www.prnewswire.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.azcentral.com/story/news/local/southwest-valley/2016/02/09/main-event-entertainment-brings-fun-all-ages-avondale/79842442/|title=Main Event Entertainment brings fun for all ages to Avondale|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.star-telegram.com/living/family/moms/maris-moments/article65447337.html|title=Main Event opens in north Fort Worth|publisher=}}</ref>

== Operations ==

=== Food and Drink ===
Each Main Event location offers restaurant services, with items like pizza, hamburgers, salads, and appetizers. Each location also has a bar, serving beer, wine, mixed drinks, and a bar menu<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.restaurantnews.com/main-event-entertainment-enhances-its-distinctive-eat-bowl-play-experience-with-new-spring-menu-041318/|title=Main Event Entertainment Enhances Its Distinctive "Eat. Bowl. Play." Experience With New Spring Menu {{!}} RestaurantNews.com|date=2018-04-13|work=RestaurantNews.com|access-date=2018-08-16|language=en-US}}</ref>.

=== Private Parties and Events ===
Main Event offers Private Party and Event space at each of their locations, as well as dedicated party planners, who help customers organize and coordinate their group events<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.visitkc.com/major-categories/event-planning-venues-and-meeting-facilities?page=6|title=Event Planning, Venues and Meeting Facilities|work=Visit KC|access-date=2018-08-16|language=en}}</ref>. Birthday, company, corporate, retirement, anniversary and other types of parties can be accommodated. Main Event also offers meeting room space and A/V capabilities for business events and hosts team building, providing facilitators and programs designed to improve communication and productivity<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.woodlandsresort.com/meetings/teambuilding/|title=The Woodlands Resort & Conference Center - Team Building|website=www.woodlandsresort.com|access-date=2018-08-16}}</ref>.

