{{italic title}} '''''Pound of Ground ''''' is an action game developed by [[Centauri Production]] and published by [[Akella]] on December 9, 2009.
==Plot and gameplay== In terms of gameplay, it is a story-driven [[shoot 'em up]] around saving the city from danger and making things right again.
==Critical reception== IGN listed off a series of weaknesses of the game including its: "unlikeable characters", "unimaginative quest goals", "bland action", "disposable story scenes", and "awful voice acting", ultimately deeming it disposible.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2010/11/11/pound-of-ground-review|title=Pound of Ground Review|first=Charles|last=Onyett|date=10 November 2010|website=ign.com|accessdate=26 March 2018}}</ref> Absolute Games offered a mixed review, citing that while the story was interesting, its gameplay let it down.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ag.ru/games/evil-days-pound-of-ground/review|title=Pound of Ground: Убитые дважды (Evil Days: Pound of Ground) - рецензия и обзор на игру на AG.ru|website=www.ag.ru|language=Russian|accessdate=26 March 2018}}</ref>
